It's all about using all of the stuff you have available.

snippet.textDisplay:
I’m slightly disappointed this was the two new variants. Half the community nearly predicted this. Would have been cooler if they just introduced something new.

I’d like to see how Furious Rajang plays out, I don’t care for Brachydios. I never liked Brachydios since he was introduced in 3U and I can’t see myself fighting his variant either. It’s just not a fun mechanic to be constantly worried about debuff pools on the ground the entire fight. Now I gotta worry about the entire map being engulfed in that shit. Definitely not looking forward to that.
